Interface Source

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Rupture>, Named
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AreaSource, ClusterSource, FaultSource, InterfaceSource, SystemSourceSet.SystemSource

    public interface Source
extends Named, Iterable<Rupture>
    An earthquake Source; usually some physical or pseudo-representation of a fault and associated IncrementalMfds governing the size and rate of all possible Ruptures.
    Author:
    Peter Powers
